debmonitor (0.5.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Hosts: automatically migrate to a new OS if needed.
  * Images: take advantage of performance optimization.
  * Allow one to save new OS names without them being present on the DB.
  * debian: run the pytest suite directly without using tox, to avoid using
            the network to pull down dependencies.
  * debian: Update control's Build-depends with the pytest dependencies.
  * debian: Override the dh_install step to avoid missing exec flags when
            evaluating .install files.
  * debian: Fix too long extended description lines (lintian warning).

 -- Luca Toscano <ltoscano@wikimedia.org>  Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:10:58 +0200

